Thank you for your dedication!!]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I came home from travel today and found 2 Ultra Vanillas in my mailbox. My pits are happy once again! Thank you, Dina!!</p>
<p>FYI: I tried a new deodorant called Peiper Wai that was on Shark Tank. Your deodorant is much better.  Peiper Wai is a dry thick paste that is difficult to apply because its so dry, and must be applied with your finger. Also, their deodorant smells earthy, versus yours which has no aroma or can be vanilla. And lastly, their&#8217;s is gray which leaves a gray film on my skin making my underarms look dirty, your does not. Also today I noticed I did sweat with Peiper Wai, however, my sweat has no smell yet my shirt is wet. With your deodorant, there is absolutely no sweat, no wetness on my shirts. Dina, you&#8217;ve created Gold!!! I say you go on Shark Tank!</p>
<p>Thank you for your dedication!!</p>
