		<pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2017 02:57:02 +0000</pubDate>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://onlygoodnessinside.com/?page_id=19#comment-17299</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[As a massage therapist, I always recommend taking an epsom salt bath with essential oils after a treatment. I’ve used many different brands of bath salts over the last 3 decades, and this is my favorite. At first I thought the scent might be a little too floral or feminine for me, but there’s something about it that brings me back to my childhood, and now I love it. I have to agree with Jessica, that the more I use it, the more I like the scent! They have figured out a wonderful blend. I just placed my 2nd order for 2 jars! I’ve also been using the deodorant for a couple of years now, and it’s ridiculous how much better and long lasting it is compared to any other deodorant I’ve tried. And the customer service is exceptional for an online store. If there’s ever a problem with a shipment, the owner is on the phone that same day explaining the situation. I noticed that they’ve expanded their product line, and I’m confident that anything I buy will be excellent.]]></description>
