		<description><![CDATA[My class had a substitute Pilates instructor who had us do a bend that messed my back up instantly. I was in pain for the rest of the day and couldn&#039;t stand up straight. I applied arnica gel a few times, did cold packs off and on, then decided to soak my back in a few heaping tablespoons of this spa kit - and the next day I had almost zero pain. I know the combination of products helped, especially this bath soak which did wonders. Thank you for this product!!! I also want to add that the scent smells pretty good but it&#039;s one that grows on you so every time I use it I think it smells more and more amazing. I will definitely repurchase.]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>My class had a substitute Pilates instructor who had us do a bend that messed my back up instantly. I was in pain for the rest of the day and couldn&#8217;t stand up straight. I applied arnica gel a few times, did cold packs off and on, then decided to soak my back in a few heaping tablespoons of this spa kit &#8211; and the next day I had almost zero pain. I know the combination of products helped, especially this bath soak which did wonders. Thank you for this product!!! I also want to add that the scent smells pretty good but it&#8217;s one that grows on you so every time I use it I think it smells more and more amazing. I will definitely repurchase.</p>
