		<pubDate>Wed, 21 Jun 2017 19:26:33 +0000</pubDate>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://onlygoodnessinside.com/?page_id=19#comment-16939</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[First day of summer and boy is it hot!  I live in Texas and from now until October we can expect more of the same.  I have been using Only Goodness Inside deodorant for over a year and it REALLY WORKS!  I am very sensitive to harsh chemicals and I even make lovely skin care products from organic carrier oils and essential oils for myself and others.  I started making my own products for personal use about 10 years ago because the store bought stuff even from health food stores was giving causing unwanted reactions.  Unfortunately I was unable to come up with an effective formula to use as a deodorant.  I found OGI online and gave it a try.  It&#039;s very impressive!  It works better than anything else I&#039;ve tried and I don&#039;t have an allergic reaction.  I especially like the formulas using essential oils because they give a subtle scent and offer some of the health benefits of the oils.  I just can&#039;t say enough GOODNESS about this product.  Thank you for consciously creating something so wonderful.  I will be a long time fan!!!]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>First day of summer and boy is it hot!  I live in Texas and from now until October we can expect more of the same.  I have been using Only Goodness Inside deodorant for over a year and it REALLY WORKS!  I am very sensitive to harsh chemicals and I even make lovely skin care products from organic carrier oils and essential oils for myself and others.  I started making my own products for personal use about 10 years ago because the store bought stuff even from health food stores was giving causing unwanted reactions.  Unfortunately I was unable to come up with an effective formula to use as a deodorant.  I found OGI online and gave it a try.  It&#8217;s very impressive!  It works better than anything else I&#8217;ve tried and I don&#8217;t have an allergic reaction.  I especially like the formulas using essential oils because they give a subtle scent and offer some of the health benefits of the oils.  I just can&#8217;t say enough GOODNESS about this product.  Thank you for consciously creating something so wonderful.  I will be a long time fan!!!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
